{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888060/extras/Wishlist.jpg?t=1717090791\" /><br><strong>Destruction Simulator</strong> is a demolition simulation game in which you take on the role of a construction worker who is tasked with tearing down several structures of varying building type and scope.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Get to work!</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888060/extras/Crane.gif?t=1717090791\" /><br>As an apprentice, your assignment is the <i>destruction of a building</i>. Watch the walls crumble beneath your mighty hammer and enjoy the collapse when you destroy the retaining walls and everything comes down upon you. You start with a small selection of construction site vehicles and equipment at your disposal. Use smaller tools to tear down the building piece by piece or come in like a wrecking ball (<strong>with</strong> a wrecking ball) to watch the whole building collapse. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888060/extras/hammersymbol.png?t=1717090791\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Finish sub-tasks and earn that money!</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888060/extras/Hammer.gif?t=1717090791\" /><br>Each work assignment consists of several alternating <strong>sub-tasks</strong> that must be completed to do a perfect job and get a <i>higher final assessment</i>. These task can very between ensuring the safety of the construction site by placing fences and moving old furniture that has been left behind out of the building. The overall assessment of your performance determines your <strong>pay</strong> for the assignment, which can be used to <strong>buy new or improved tools</strong>.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888060/extr